Mainly used for photo editing, sketching, and digital drawing for experts , Accessories Fully Packed:  Along with the UGEE M708 Drawing Tablet and Pen Stylus, you will also get a Pen Stand, 8 Pen Nibs(Inside the Pen Stand), Nib Replace Ring( Inside the Pen Stand), a 2-finger Glove, a Normal Gloves, Cleaning Brush, Cleaning Cloth.
